To create the classes and layouts for the activities you mentioned, you can follow these steps. I'll provide a basic structure for each Java class and mention the corresponding XML layout file you should create.

### Java Classes

1. **MainActivity.java (or SplashActivity.java)**
   ```java
   package com.vantinh.tienganh;

